==Links of Interest== ===Linux driver support=== *[http://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?t=2221847 Post on '''Ubuntu Forums''' w/ lsusb output] :The USB ID is 050d:110a, the same as the F9L1101v2 *[https://github.com/lwfinger/rtl8192du/issues/17 ''Issue #17'' on the '''rtl8192du''' git repo] references this device ===Vendor links=== *[http://www.target.com/p/belkin-dual-band-wifi-usb-adapter-black-f9l1108-tg/-/A-14447571 F9L1108-TG @ '''target.com''']
